Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:05.31,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Oww... {For episode 9, 10 and 11, consider "orders" vs "mission" for Narancia.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:08.61,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Yeah, you'll need to go to the hospital for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:12.95,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,No shit I will! \N Just patch me up before then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.24,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:18.08,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Fugo, what are you{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.54,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.75,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,What did you do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:25.04,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Staples!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:27.38,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,It's actually sealed up \N like a comic book!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.96,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Narancia, could you wrap his stomach \N with some gummed tape for me? {it's gummed tape and we're not changing it fuck you -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:31.80,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.59,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,This isn't gonna get infected, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:36.30,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:38.05,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Y'know, this actually kinda works!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:39.56,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Could you keep it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:43.35,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Good job, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:47.69,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Because of your efforts, \N we safely reached Capri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.90,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The assailant, Zucchero, \N and the man Mista took out... {Starfish will remember this... -J}{Starfish will indeed remember it. ARGH IT STILL LOOKS LIKE HE'S REFERRING TO THREE PEOPLE WHEN HE IS ACTUALLY REFERRING TO TWO BECAUSE "THE ASSAILANT" WAS ZUCCHERO. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:54.65,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...are both passed out on the boat. \N They won't be bothering us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:59.37,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Then take us to where \N you hid the ten billion lire already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:01.66,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Where'd you hide it, Buccellati?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:03.75,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Inside a hidden bank vault?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.83,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Or buried in some cave \N here on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.17,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Could you wait just a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.71,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:15.30,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Why does it matter when you tell us?
Comment: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:16.68,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:23.31,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Hey, fellas. \N We're still in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:25.85,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Why don'tcha save the cleaning for later?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:29.31,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,Does your name happen to be Toilette?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:32.03,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:37.70,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,If your name is Toilette, \N this must be where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:41.03,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,You can call the shots \N if this is your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:46.21,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,But if it's {\i1}not{\i0} your house, \N you have no right ordering me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.17,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Huh? \N Hey, wait, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.96,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me? \N I said we're still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.85,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.97,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}You want a piece of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:02.35,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,What?{I see no reason why this and the next line overlapped. So I have un-overlapped them. -Starfish the guy who so far has made a whole bunch of non-translation-related nitpicks yet no actual translation corrections}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:02.97,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Another enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.97,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I'll fucking kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.14,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.90,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Everyone, stop Narancia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:08.90,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why are you stopping me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.27,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,These two may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:13.86,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:15.61,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.16,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Everyone, bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:23.33,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,This is one of the capos of Passione: \N Mr. Pericolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:26.20,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,I'm here for the ten billion lire...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.41,Main,Pericolo,0,0,0,,...Buccellati.
Comment: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Opening
